The computation of the Gâteaux derivative of Eqs. (1) and (2) yields a necessary condition for \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
